Description: Limestone ostracon: on the recto ten lines of a duplicate text of P.Anastasi I, 1,1 - 1,4. On the verso some trial strokes of a brush only.
Curator's comments: Bibliography: H.-W.Fischer-Elfert, 'Die Satirische Streitschrift des Papyrus Anastasi' I, ‘Kleine ägyptische Texte’ (2nd edn, Wiesbaden 1992), pp.4 (no.80) and 9-17.
Bibliographic references: Trismegistos / An interdisciplinary portal of papyrological and epigraphic resources (393036) (http://www.trismegistos.org/text/393036)
